{"article_id":"2Ndl2JDTEfgEpJ83","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"As Democrats call for gun reform in the wake of the deadliest shooting in modern US history ,","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"will Trump offer divisive rhetoric or a willingness","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"to cross the aisle ?","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Donald Trump faces a test of temperament on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"as he visits Las Vegas , the scene of the deadliest mass shooting in modern US history ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"with Democrats stepping up political pressure for tighter gun laws .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"It has become a grim ritual for American presidents to visit the scenes of mass murder and gun violence ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"burdened by expectations","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that they will be dignified ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"rise above party politics","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"and perform the unifying role of head of state .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"But Trump is already notorious for divisive rhetoric at key national moments ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"including after the racially charged violence in Charlottesville , Virginia , in August .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The National Rifle Association was crucial to his election","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and he was the first sitting president since Ronald Reagan","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"to address its annual conference ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"where he vowed to defend the second amendment .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"Gun control :","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Trump says","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"lawmakers will discuss issue","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"'as time goes by '","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Read more","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"Since the gunman ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"identified by police as Stephen Paddock ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"opened fire from his hotel room ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"killing at least 59 victims","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"and injuring more than 500 at a country music festival on Sunday night ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Trump has struck a measured tone .","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"But on the ground in Las Vegas ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"where he is expected to meet the state governor and city mayor ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"and possibly visit survivors in hospital ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"there will be no shortage of opportunities for a jarring remark .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"On Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"visiting hurricane hit Puerto Rico ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"he joked :","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"\" I hate to tell you , Puerto Rico ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"but you ' ve thrown our budget a little out of whack .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"But that ' s fine","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"because we ' ve saved a lot of lives . \"","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Democrats intend to throw down the gauntlet","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"before Trump ' s plane touches down","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"by staging a high-profile event on the front steps of the US Capitol building in Washington .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"Congressman and civil rights veteran John Lewis and former congresswoman Gabby Giffords ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"who survived a shooting in 2011 ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"will be among those","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"calling for the immediate passage of legislation","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"to strengthen background checks on gun buyers ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"as well as creating a bipartisan select committee on gun violence .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"In a Republican-controlled Congress , Democrats know","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"the odds are against them .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"But they think","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"they may have an unlikely ally in Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"whose views on gun control have shifted","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"since he ran for president as a Republican .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Past incidents","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"- such as visceral TV images of children","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"killed by poison gas in Syria -","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"suggest","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"that Trump can be swayed by direct appeals to the heart .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"On Tuesday the president said :","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"\" We ' ll be talking about gun laws","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"as time goes by . \"","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"In a floor speech , Chuck Schumer , the Senate minority leader , called on Trump to bring together leaders of Congress as a sign to both sides","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"that he is \" ready and willing to address this issue of gun safety head-on \" .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Activists and even comedians have called on Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"who ran as an anti-Washington outsider ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"to act .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Late-night TV host Stephen Colbert said :","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"\" You do not owe the Republicans anything .","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"You know","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"the Republicans tried to stop you from being president ;","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"well screw ' em .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"You want to make America great again ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"do something","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"the last two presidents have been unable to do :","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"pass any kind of commonsense gun control legislation","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"that the vast majority of Americans want . \"","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"Democrats are weary from years of political stalemate over gun control .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Senator Chris Murphy , from Connecticut , was visibly frustrated on Tuesday","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"when he condemned members ' \" utter silence \" in response to ever-rising toll of mass shootings","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"and called their inaction \" unintentional complicity \" .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"A perennial American question :","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"why has gun control failed ?","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Read more","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"\" In the minds of these mad men","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"when they see Congress doing absolutely nothing ,","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"shooting after shooting -","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"they read that as quiet acceptance of the carnage , \"","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"Murphy told reporters on Capitol Hill .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"\" It has to stop . \"","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Joined by four colleagues ,","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"the Democratic senators outlined \" a menu \" of gun control measures","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"they planned to introduce ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"including to expand background checks and to restrict people","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"convicted of domestic violence","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"from obtaining a gun .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Senator Dianne Feinstein of California also plans to reintroduce a bill","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"that would ban bump stocks and similar devices ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"which","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"Murphy said","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"he believes","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"could attract bipartisan support .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Senator Bob Casey , a Democrat of Pennsylvania , cited himself as an example of how one incident can change hearts and minds .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"Before the 2012 massacre of 26 young children and teachers in Newtown , Connecticut , Casey opposed additional gun restrictions .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"he realised then","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"that opposing the slate of gun control measures","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"brought forward that session","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"meant accepting that nothing could change .","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"He said :","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"\" I think","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"we have to ask ourselves the same question again .","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"Is there nothing","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"that we can do ?","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"No law ?","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"Nothing","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"that we can do ? ...","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"I don ' t think","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"that ' s acceptable . \"","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"But there has been little sign that the horror of Las Vegas will budge congressional Republicans .","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"The Senate majority leader , Mitch McConnell , dismissed the debate as \" premature \"","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"and chastised Democrats","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"for raising the issue of gun control so soon after the attack .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"it ' s particularly inappropriate to politicize an event like this , \"","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"McConnell said .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"\" It just happened within the last day and a half .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"It ' s entirely premature to be discussing legislative solutions","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"- if any . \"","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"He added :","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"\" We ' re in the middle of an investigation .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"We ' ll see what that reveals","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"and at the end of that will be an appropriate time","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"to discuss it .","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"In the meantime , our priority is tax reform . \"","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"Schumer also called on Republicans to drop a bill","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"that would make it easier to purchase a silencer .","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"Republicans postponed a hearing on the bill in June","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"when members were attacked by a gunman during a congressional baseball practice .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"\" When two mass shootings force you to delay a bill","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"that would make those mass shootings harder to detect and stop ,","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"maybe that ' s a sign","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"you ought to let go of the bill , once and for all , \"","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"On Tuesday , Ryan said","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"the bill was not currently scheduled to come to the floor .","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"The deeply entrenched partisan divide on gun control are illustrated by two former House colleagues","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"who were both grievously injured in mass shootings .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"Play Video 0:40","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"Donald Trump calls Las Vegas gunman 'demented ' - video","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"Congressman Steve Scalise on Tuesday joined his Republican colleagues for a weekly press conference .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"It was his first time at the podium","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"since returning to Washington","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"after he was grievously injured in the June shooting .","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"Scalise urged prayer","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"and did not raise the issue of gun control .","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"In a Fox News interview later on Tuesday , Martha MacCallum asked Scalise","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"if his experience","depth":15},{"id":158,"text":"being shot on a baseball diamond","depth":15},{"id":159,"text":"had changed his views on the Second Amendment ,","depth":15},{"id":160,"text":"which guarantees the right of citizens","depth":16},{"id":161,"text":"to \" bear arms \" .","depth":16},{"id":162,"text":"Scalise , a strong supporter of gun rights , replied :","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"\" I think","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"it ' s fortified it . \"","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"Scalise is one of only a handful of members of Congress","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"who have been injured","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"while serving in office .","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"Another is Giffords , now a prominent advocate for stricter gun control .","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"Paddock had an arsenal of 23 guns in his suite on the 32nd floor of the Mandalay Bay Hotel .","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"The retiree had no criminal record","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"and his motive remains a mystery","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"as the criminal investigation continues .","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"On Tuesday Sheriff Joseph Lombardo of Clark County said","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"detectives were in contact with 64-year-old Paddock ' s girlfriend Marilou Danley ,","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"who is in the Philippines","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"and considered \" a person of interest \" .","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"Trump has described Paddock as a \" very , very sick individual \"","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"\" we ' re looking into him very seriously . \"","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":359,"left":182,"right":358,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":182,"left":0,"right":181,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":181,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":358,"left":217,"right":357,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":217,"left":200,"right":216,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":200,"left":195,"right":199,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":195,"left":184,"right":194,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":3,"right":183,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":188,"right":193,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"